{"tid":1251673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[脫歐之戰] 圍警總後戰略部署","createTime":"2019-06-22T15:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T02:21:29.000Z","uid":81716,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5b7967bdb3246d452b34b8b92cf4e6c63c9915","tid":1251673,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"之前有個po講脫歐之戰可以睇下<br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 電影《脫歐：無理之戰》教晒我哋點贏民意<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246299\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246299</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今次中間派被影響到既係CCTVB，你睇番RTHK32同埋NOW，示威者係讓左條路出黎，係d狗唔開門<br />\n<br />\n脫歐之戰有個位講得好岩<br />\n1/3 反對派<br />\n1/3 支持派<br />\n1/3 中間遊離派<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對同支持派不論你點搞都係鐵票，你搞唔到佢，唔會因為一兩單新聞就逆轉，所謂民意被逆轉既族群就係中間遊離派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而呢種派別，佢地係不問世事，喜愛玩樂，打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />非常容易受別人影響<br />\n<br />\n套戲入面用得最成功既大戰略係，要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">影響呢類族群就係用情感（emotional)，不能用理性，佢地都唔中意諗野，你同佢地講理性，道理有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以講既野係假都唔緊要，佢地照單全收，佢地係識諗野既話就唔會成為中間派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n由此，如何去表達一件事情就好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">CCTVB用煽情方法，將警犬當係受害者角</span></strong></span>色，希望中間派同情，我地就要逆轉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1。 唔係我地唔開路啊，係佢地唔開門炸<br />\n<br />\n2。 我地係手無寸鐵既市民，但班警察起入面涼冷氣，都唔肯出黎傾，出面成三十幾度啊，仲抖住人工望住我地受苦<br />\n<br />\n3。仲有啊，你諗下徹回咪大家無事囉，一哥都咁講（雖然佢無咁講，但套戲教你真真假假d人唔concern，都逼到佢地分化，一哥最終又要出黎講野，一講野又分）<br />\n<br />\n4。 長輩圖，youtube 長輩片，唔洗講啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5。 Lost focus <br />\n<br />\n起一d對方根本贏硬既主場同佢地打就係送頭，要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">引佢地入不知不覺間入去死地，盡量避免起佢地贏既位同佢地打</span></span> from 孫子兵法-九地篇<br />\n<br />\n一講示威者擲磚，我地就講番警察用左過度武力<br />\n<br />\n警總外建議，播一哥同佢地割席既片，有無得諗？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1248247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1248247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織重申：警方做法有違國際標準 要求成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n佢地話示威者挑釁，咁我地就播番黑警講屌你老母同舉中指<br />\n<br />\n我地已經有巴打做緊野<br />\n<br />\n然而，中間遊離派就係一個極易受到煽動既族群，而CCTVB 就係不論你點做佢都一定會煽動，點樣反擊暫時就列左呢幾點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">社會上面一路強調既逆轉民意只係一班唔經大腦諗野，容易受感情，情感影響既中立派，所以點樣表達到一件事，令到風向往我地呢邊先係重點，每件事係睇你點去表達多於話件事係岩定錯</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣做得好，錯都可以變成岩，岩都變成錯<br />\n<br />\n所以隔離有個PO做故仔係做得非常岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認同請分享"},{"pid":"5f6bd1f4575d67cbba2badee043d36b40286f5b0","tid":1251673,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:44:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f02a0bcebd57af1f9934150286104228cecd2f6d","tid":1251673,"uid":81716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aea08ddc2b88e5ed6001be5839e1eec36211e380","tid":1251673,"uid":181585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c61c62151a35fe7ce5ef76313f5bae8603761217","tid":1251673,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"問題係冇腦人士都係睇黨媒<br />\n人地既優勢係度, <br />\n當然, 唔可以犯大錯<br />\n圍警總唔好再搞啦, 一錯就清袋<br />\n群眾既野, 唔知邊個癲起上黎, 或者啲混入黎搞事既衝左入去警總, 比政府告你搶軍火你就仆街"},{"pid":"f8fda9b8d2778b60f501963107ee722941418220","tid":1251673,"uid":132770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"去探一哥😏"},{"pid":"6d7294e607fcc17de216ea31cbbde6ed925df3b8","tid":1251673,"uid":264780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分化藍絲 逆向洗腦文宣行動!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246317</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反送中長輩圖製作技巧分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251336</a>"},{"pid":"a23a520ba8b4dab61c06546b0beed5869b849454","tid":1251673,"uid":198258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"街站播片好過派傳單，班師奶廢老根本就睇唔明/睇唔會睇，點解cctvb咁洗腦係因為佢易入口，有畫面唔洗自己思考。"},{"pid":"b0716746df51b1b8b9e3c3a31e34615ae30d9622","tid":12516